data.description: Newly Renovated Ranch Overlooking the Black River! New lighting, flooring, central air, and other upgrades abound in this stunning home located just minutes to Carthage, Watertown, & Fort Drum. Step inside a large foyer with lots of storage into a sunny & spacious living room. The adjacent eat-in kitchen features butcher block counters, stainless appliances, and walk-in pantry for extra storage. Down the hall are 3 updated bedrooms and a full bath, including a main bedroom suite with its own bath and custom closet. Outside you'll find a private lot surrounded by trees, a 2-stall attached garage, and serene views of the River across the street. Whether it's the convenient location or renovated interior, this home has it all! Contact an agent today for details, or to schedule a private showing.
